  "excerpt": "I tend to get obsessed with things. Right now I am pretty obsessed with the sweater from Cents of Style . I'll be wearing it at least once a week, so if you see me in real life in the…",
  "legacyPath": "/blog/2016/11/28/holla-a-new-drone",
